'''明尼苏达式友善'''（{{lang-en|Minnesota nice}}），是指[[美国|美国]][[明尼苏达州|明尼苏达州]]人民热情友善的待人方式。

按照Annette Atkins的说法，明尼苏达式友善的特征包括了待人处事时的礼貌，对于冲突的厌恶，互相理解，律己和自嘲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csbsju.edu/History/Faculty/Annette-Atkins.htm|title=Annette Atkins|work=History Department|publisher={{cite web|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/College_of_Saint_Benedict_and_Saint_John's_University|title=College of Saint Benedict and Saint John's University}}|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100928041510/http://www.csbsju.edu/History/Faculty/Annette-Atkins.htm|archivedate=2010-09-28}}</ref>。

